---
import BaseLayout from '../components/layout/BaseLayout.astro';

const canonicalURL = new URL('/about', Astro.site).toString();
---

<BaseLayout
  title="About YAAWA"
  description="YAAWA (You Ask And We Answer) helps couples make wedding decisions with confidence through clear, balanced, practical answers."
  canonicalURL={canonicalURL}
>
  <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 py-16">
    <div class="mb-12">
      <h1 class="font-display text-5xl font-bold text-charcoal mb-6">
        About YAAWA
      </h1>
      <p class="text-2xl font-display font-light text-charcoal-light italic">
        You Ask. We Answer.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="prose-answer space-y-6">
      <p class="text-lg text-charcoal leading-relaxed">
        Planning a wedding means making hundreds of decisions, often for the first time, while navigating strong opinions from every direction. YAAWA exists to give couples a place to find clear, honest, balanced answers to the questions that actually matter.
      </p>

      <h2>Our Mission</h2>
      <p>
        Help couples make wedding decisions with confidence. Not by telling them what to do — but by giving them the information, context, and balanced perspectives they need to decide for themselves.
      </p>

      <h2>Where the Questions Come From</h2>
      <p>
        Our questions are sourced from real conversations — the debates, dilemmas, and genuine uncertainties that couples share online every day. We focus on the questions people actually have, not the ones wedding industry content assumes they should have.
      </p>

      <h2>How We Write Answers</h2>
      <p>
        Every answer on YAAWA follows the same philosophy:
      </p>
      <ul>
        <li>Answer the question directly and immediately</li>
        <li>Provide balanced perspectives — traditional etiquette, modern thinking, and practical reality</li>
        <li>Avoid clickbait and manufactured controversy</li>
        <li>Be practical, not preachy</li>
        <li>Feel like advice from an experienced wedding planner who genuinely cares</li>
      </ul>

      <h2>What We Are Not</h2>
      <p>
        YAAWA is not a vendor marketplace. We don't sell listings or take commissions. We don't push particular services, brands, or approaches. Our only goal is helping you make good decisions.
      </p>

      <div class="mt-12 bg-champagne/40 border border-champagne rounded-xl p-8">
        <h2 class="font-display text-2xl font-bold text-charcoal mb-2">Our Promise</h2>
        <p class="text-charcoal leading-relaxed">
          Clear answers to wedding questions. Every time. No agenda, no judgment, no pressure. Just the honest, practical information you need to plan your wedding your way.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>
